### OpenAI Chat Completions API with History
POST {{AIAgent.Host_HostAddress}}/ContosoTravelAgent/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi! I'm planning my next adventure and would love some help."
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Hello! It's great to meet you. I'd be happy to help you plan your next adventure. To provide you with the best recommendations, could you tell me:\n\n1. What kind of experiences are you hoping for on this trip?\n2. Do you have a budget in mind for this adventure?\n3. How would you describe your travel style?\n\nThis will help me suggest the perfect destination for your adventure!"
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I love snorkeling and diving. Looking to travel in March for about a week. Budget around 4000 AUD"
    }
  ]
}